{"tid":1087802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖][清純可人]泰國清純學生妹甜笑好迷人","createTime":"2019-04-01T14:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T01:49:42.000Z","uid":172616,"like":8,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9263a005c45430d3301b7b628d8790275a49ea","tid":1087802,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"泰國社交媒體上最近流傳了一系列的學生相，相中的女生有著瘦削的身型，以及雪白細膩的肌膚，最重要的是笑起來的時候，有一種清純可愛的氣質，不少人都指她有一種初戀的感覺！不過，這個女學生是穿著男生的校服，難道他是.....?<br />\n    這個可愛的「女學生」Peerada Namwong，其實是來自泰國曼谷挽叻易三倉中學，這是一間男校，不過由於他擁有精緻的五官，以及那個清純又可愛的笑容，加上他不時會戴假髮，不少人都以為他是女生。<br />\n    不過，即使把假髮脫下，他的外表和神韻，都猶如一個小女生般，所以不少網民都指，他有一種初戀的感覺！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82641889902654ff79ce34af13e9eb87c97e0605","tid":1087802,"uid":199162,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"是個Boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce54130678c05bd4c7fd1f3d04490c444f97f3ec","tid":1087802,"uid":172616,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會成為男校肉便器，日日戴假髮著女裝畀人輪住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1dbe2f0fc9e4db81ad8e58a2ba3c6c0c4aa354","tid":1087802,"uid":172616,"like":48,"dislike":16,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"想知巴打們寧願屌哩種仔，定係屌成個男人咁嘅女人<br />\n<br />\n屌仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌男人婆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be7bc3b4208a2a3cf8c5c9c2b1cb3b8aeebf052","tid":1087802,"uid":181680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"泰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe9459d28233329497ef7a502358ec4d0ed352","tid":1087802,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be7bc3b4208a2a3cf8c5c9c2b1cb3b8aeebf052","tid":1087802,"uid"